  "texts": [
    "For example, Neuron Shapley applies SV to identify the model neurons that are most critical for a given prediction (Ghorbani & Zou, 2020).",
    "Lundberg & Lee's (2017) SHAP is a very well-known tool that applies SV to measure feature importance.",
    "For a comprehensive survey of Shapley value applications beyond training data influence, see the work of Sundararajan & Najmi (2020) and a more recent update by Rozemberczki et al. (2022).",
    "(25) kNN (D) ∶= -",
    "Banzhaf value Also a semivalue (Dubey et al., 1981), Banzhaf value (Banzhaf, 1965) is closely related to Shapley value."
  ]
